name: Vorka Virus (Transition Form)
description:
Second form of the AntiMetro Vorka.

To decimate human civilization, Vorka must become more violent than just a computer virus. It slowly evolves into a biological weapon harmful enough to infect humans.

Featuring BGM by Fabian Winandi. This second part still speaks of death and suffering, but with a hint of beauty.

Collectors of BOTH Transition form and Digital form have a chance to get the final form for free.
